  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Media campaigns supporting the task Economic Security of the Elderly in Moldova (TF0A0948)</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="3">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Older People, of Pension age</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The objective of this assignment is to contribute to the work on Economic Security of the Elderly in Moldova, and policy options for strengthening it. As Moldova struggles with the challenges of a fast ageing population, it is key to explore the situation of Moldova&apos;s elderly in relation to their right to social and economic security, and create knowledge that can inform policy options to guarantee an adequate living standard for the elderly. The activity is motivated by a human rights-based approach to aging and the elderly population.</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This specific component of the grant aims at informing the population about the provisions of the current pension legislation, so that they understand their own entitlements under the new pension law.</narrative>
  </description>
